Package entities.trees

Class Tree_Query_Solution

  • java.lang.Object
    • entities.trees.TDP_Solution
      • entities.trees.Tree_Query_Solution
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Comparable<Tree_Query_Solution>
    public class Tree_Query_Solution
extends TDP_Solution
implements Comparable<Tree_Query_Solution>
    A T-DP solution for problems that are equi-join acyclic (tree) queries. The solution thus consists of database tuples. Implements the abstract methods of TDP_Solution. Used by Tree_Batch.
    Author:
    Nikolaos Tziavelis
